Overwatch League Stage 3 Week 2 in 90 Seconds
videos.description: Uber brings you the top stories and a quick recap of Stage 3 Week 2 in 90 seconds!

videos.title: Dallas Fuel Finally Has OGE
videos.description: Meet the newest member of the Dallas Fuel, OGE. He talks about the excitement of joining the team and how contributing to the team to make it more successful makes it worth it.

videos.title: Dynasty Welcomes Gambler
videos.description: We meet the newest member for Seoul Dynasty, Gambler. He shares his Overwatch League rise, learning from his teammates on how to improve his performance, and being the teams new shot-caller.

videos.title: Will Valiant Fly Over Gladiators?
videos.description: Los Angeles Valiants Agilities and Custa along with Los Angeles Gladiators Bischu and silkthread stake their claim on Part 3 of Battle for LA.

videos.title: Emote Control  Miros Facepalm Moment
videos.description: This week on Emote Control, Houston Outlaws Rawkus is sick, Seoul Dynastys Miro has a facepalm moment, Philadelphia Fusions Poko stops mid-game to play another game, and more!

videos.title: Boston Uprising Exposes NYXL
videos.description: The Boston Uprising talk about their recent challenges, how theyre focusing on everyones strengths, and most recently how they figured out New York Excelsiors weakness.

videos.title: We Didnt See These Plays Coming
videos.description: Monte, Mr. X, and Uber bring you this weeks most clutch plays from Poko, Sayaplayer, Fissure, and more that we never saw coming!

videos.title: Dallas Fuels KyKy is Gone
videos.description: Monte, Mr. X, and Uber talk about the recent news about Dallas Fuel releasing Rascal and Head Coach KyKy, and what might happen next for the team.

Emote Control  Gamsus Set Up Rules
videos.description: The team brings you this weeks Emote Control and talks the epic entrance for the Philadelphia Fusion, Boston Uprising Gamsus intense set up, and Los Angeles Gladiator Fissures primal fail.

videos.title: New rivals: Houston Outlaws and London Spitfire
videos.description: London Spitfire has found their weakness, and its the Houston Outlaws. Gesture and Profit discuss how Houston doesnt have a conventional strategy and a rivalry would only fuel their passion to win the Overwatch League.

videos.title: 3 Week 1 in 90 Seconds!
videos.description: Shanghai Dragons introduce new players, Los Angeles Valiant picks up a winner, San Francisco Shock and their young guns, and New York Excelsiors Pine is back in action!

videos.title: Los Angeles Valiant Looks Forward to The Future
videos.description: Los Angeles Valiants Head Coach, Byung Chul MBC Moon, talks about what changes he sees for the future, and the potential he saw in making some changes within the team.

videos.title: Fissure, Bdosin, and Effect Put It All On The Table
videos.description: Los Angeless Fissure explains the 3 types of professional gamers, what London Spitfires Bdosin wants for the future, and how Effect is the only active Korean player on the Dallas Fuels roster.

videos.title: Philadelphia Fusion Shuts Down London Spitfire
videos.description: We look back on the epic battle from Stage 2 Overwatch League Title Matches between Philadelphia Fusion and London Spitfire.

videos.title: Meet The New Shanghai Dragons!
videos.description: We sit down with the new pros on the Shanghai Dragons.
